{"id":14484,"date":"2023-07-08T16:16:05","date_gmt":"2023-07-08T09:16:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14484"},"modified":"2023-07-08T16:16:05","modified_gmt":"2023-07-08T09:16:05","slug":"hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid  &#8220;\u0103n&#8221; h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km"},"content":{"rendered":"<article class=\"singular-container\">\n<div class=\"singular-content\">\n<p>Sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e9 l\u1ed9, TC Motor \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n hybrid c\u1ee7a Hyundai Santa Fe \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t. M\u1eabu CUV n\u00e0y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean xe chuy\u00ean ch\u1edf v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dantri.com.vn\/su-kien.htm\" data-auto-link-id=\"612dcf9bfb044100119a1417\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-autolink\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-autolink_612dcf9bfb044100119a1417\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\">s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/a>\u00a0n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, sau khi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1eafp r\u00e1p v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159474.jpeg\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Santa Fe Hybrid thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 h\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng &#8220;lai&#8221; g\u1ed3m: \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng SmartStream 1.6L t\u0103ng \u00e1p (178 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c\/265Nm) \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 van bi\u1ebfn thi\u00ean li\u00ean t\u1ee5c CVVD, m\u1ed9t m\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n (60 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c\/264Nm) v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 pin 1.49kWh. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kia Sorento Hybrid s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tr\u00ean cho ra t\u1ed5ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 227 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 350Nm. Theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a TC Motor, Santa Fe Hybrid c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u kho\u1ea3ng 5,01 cho 100km trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 2\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 2\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg\" data-photo-id=\"2528641\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528641\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\" data-src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159702.jpeg 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid c\u1ee7a Santa Fe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb chung v\u1edbi Kia Sorento (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 3\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 3\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png\" data-photo-id=\"2528642\" data-width=\"1582\" data-height=\"557\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528642\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\" data-src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093159894.png 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Hyundai Santa Fe t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Xe d\u00f9ng h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 6 c\u1ea5p, h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ed1n b\u00e1nh to\u00e0n th\u1eddi gian HTRAC t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn b\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc &#8211; sau t\u1eeb 100:0 \u0111\u1ebfn 50:50 t\u00f9y theo \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Xe v\u1eabn c\u00f3 4 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i l\u00e0 Eco (Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m), Comfort (Tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i), Sport (Th\u1ec3 thao) v\u00e0 Smart (Th\u00f4ng minh).<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 4\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 4\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg\" data-photo-id=\"2528643\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528643\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\" data-src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160563.jpeg 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>HTRAC c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn linh ho\u1ea1t (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u1eaec-quy 12V \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea5m l\u00f3t c\u1ed1p sau thay v\u00ec trong khoang \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c nh\u1eb1m nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng, Santa Fe Hybrid c\u00f2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Active Shift Control (gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ec5 khi chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1) hay E-Handling (t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n xe trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di chuy\u1ec3n qua c\u00e1c g\u00f3c cua).<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 5\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 5\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg\" data-photo-id=\"2528644\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528644\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\" data-src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160781.jpeg 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>Santa Fe Hybrid c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh t\u00e2n ti\u1ebfn (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1eabn danh s\u00e1ch trang b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n Hybrid gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ec7t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.2 D\u1ea7u Cao c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 &#8220;option&#8221; n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e8n Full-LED tr\u01b0\u1edbc-sau, la-z\u0103ng 19 inch, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng 10.25 inch h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Apple CarPlay\/Android Auto, 10 loa Harman Kardon, c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1eddi to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh, s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y chu\u1ea9n Qi, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111i k\u00e8m nh\u1edb 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho gh\u1ebf l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u01b0\u1edfi\/th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 gh\u1ebf, l\u1eaby chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 sau v\u00f4-l\u0103ng v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean k\u00ednh l\u00e1i (HUD).<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 d\u1ea1ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 12,3 inch gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid thay v\u00ec v\u00f2ng tua m\u00e1y.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 6\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160989.jpeg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160989.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160989.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160989.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 6\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093160989.jpeg\" data-photo-id=\"2528645\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528645\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xan