ta-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161249.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161249.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161249.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161249.jpeg 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid tr\u00ean Santa Fe (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dantri.com.vn\/chu-de\/hyundai-thanh-cong-4136.htm\" data-auto-link-id=\"6464892490339bade1b997ae\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-autolink\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-autolink_6464892490339bade1b997ae\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\">Hyundai<\/a>\u00a0Santa Fe Hybrid c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u00e0 g\u00f3i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 SmartSense v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng nh\u01b0: ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m khi l\u00f9i, gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u00e8n pha t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111i t\u1edbi khi m\u1edf c\u1eeda. Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb 6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed, camera 360 \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u1ed1p.<\/p>\n<p>Santa Fe Hybrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh 5 n\u0103m ho\u1eb7c 100.000 km (t\u00f9y \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc).<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"entered loaded\" title=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 8\" src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 2x\" alt=\"Hyundai Santa Fe Hybrid gi\u00e1 1,450 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0103n h\u01a1n 5 l\u00edt x\u0103ng cho 100km - 8\" data-original=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg\" data-photo-id=\"2528647\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2528647\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\" data-src=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/680\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 1x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1020\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 1.5x, https:\/\/icdn.dantri.com.vn\/thumb_w\/1360\/2023\/06\/30\/hyunda-santa-fe-hybriddocx-1688093161480.jpeg 2x\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" \/><figcaption>Sau Kia Sorento, Hyundai Santa Fe l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe ti\u1ebfp theo trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac c\u00f3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n hybrid (\u1ea2nh: TC Motor).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Hyundai Santa Fe t\u1eebng l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac trong n\u0103m 2022, v\u1edbi doanh s\u1ed1 10.603 chi\u1ebfc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft th\u00fac 5 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2023, Hyundai ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1.991 chi\u1ebfc CUV n\u00e0y, k\u00e9m xa\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dantri.com.vn\/tim-kiem\/ford+everest.htm\" data-auto-link-id=\"5ff2b27eb00b7a0012bca1fb\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-autolink\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-autolink_5ff2b27eb00b7a0012bca1fb\" data-content-target=\"\/o-to-xe-may\/hyundai-santa-fe-hybrid-gia-1450-ty-dong-an-hon-5-lit-xang-cho-100km-20230630095102410.htm\">Ford Everest<\/a>\u00a0(3.898 chi\u1ebfc).<\/p>\n<p>Gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m nay, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Hyundai Santa Fe b\u1ea3n D\u1ea7u Cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m 2022 (VIN 2022), \u0111\u01b0a gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1eeb 1,375 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1,075 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m 50% ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1\/7 \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua s\u1ebd ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng g\u1ea7n 370 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng &#8211; t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc Toyota Wigo b\u1ea3n E.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/article>\n<div class=\"singular-footer\" data-module=\"social-pin\"><\/div>\n<div data-module=\"reaction-object\" data-object-id=\"20230630095102410\">\n<div class=\"lazyload-wrapper \"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>